{"tid":2266609,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"告別71吧 老闆：有人就有希望","createTime":"2020-11-01T12:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T12:32:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"069c9f2fa2073a56330e6a10a052b8d76f8966f7","tid":2266609,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/KRDA3LTSWZEXRC5YLMMJBEO6VQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FKRDA3LTSWZEXRC5YLMMJBEO6VQ%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh7%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=5d35325a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FKRDA3LTSWZEXRC5YLMMJBEO6VQ%2F&h=ae45d565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/KRDA3LTSWZEXRC5YLMMJBEO6VQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n告別71吧 老闆：有人就有希望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HvIig2Vw7jwgyUll3SMxD8rJBVw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BHRDO3JCIVHILDWF5GWVK4HHBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHvIig2Vw7jwgyUll3SMxD8rJBVw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBHRDO3JCIVHILDWF5GWVK4HHBI.jpg&h=f342569e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■最後一夜的71吧座無虛席，席間有人高舉五一手勢。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人聲鼎沸根本不足以形容最後一夜的71吧，買酒的人龍，一直排到轉角處陰暗的樓梯，喝得臉紅耳熱的人們站滿酒吧外和前面的百子里公園，甚至沒有可以轉身的空間。有燈就有人，老闆娘馬麗華勉勵大家無謂傷感，「只要有人就有希望」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TOUtjZ30Q5J2JsblaKsuPYBzzdw=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3WFJTYJETNC2JBOWL6ONXKVFIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTOUtjZ30Q5J2JsblaKsuPYBzzdw%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3WFJTYJETNC2JBOWL6ONXKVFIE.jpg&h=252fe880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬麗華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店長勉勵熟客「總有日重遇」<br />\n<br />\n集合文藝與社運元素於一身的香港人酒吧71吧結業，昨晚最後一天營業，新知舊雨四方八面湧來，有人悲情話別，有人笑看風雲。常客David整晚跟朋友坐在一旁聊天，由64吧開始到今天，光顧了差不多30年，兩個地方最大分別就是相比當年在蘭桂坊的64吧，71吧位置難找，必須穿過暗巷，才能柳暗花明，「心情無奈，好多難忘事，見過人喺呢度打架、相戀，又識咗好多朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n昨晚有很多是熟客，但更多是第一次來的，就如東區區議員趙家賢，一。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n忙得頭也昏的小萍，沒時間傷春悲秋，拋下一句「呢度係我第二個家，係一個畀人唞氣嘅地方，就算放假我都約朋友返嚟飲嘢。」當。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有燈就有人，71吧尚未油盡燈枯，老闆娘馬麗華在最後一夜遇見新歡舊友，酩。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n沒有傷感，卻有憤怒，她感慨香港的業主有無窮的慾望，「佢以為我仇富，我一啲都唔仇富，係社會資源分配不均，先會有革命！」緣起緣滅，她說人生路上有起跌，暫時停下來，也許是讓她能走更長的路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FCaupTWNMgEciExvUub77eAI9aQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RE6YDVUGOJHQJLNDAMBLNHP4SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFCaupTWNMgEciExvUub77eAI9aQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRE6YDVUGOJHQJLNDAMBLNHP4SE.jpg&h=55b5635c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■顧客站滿酒吧對出的百子里公園。"},{"pid":"522a8ad648cda17e8c1d8a385d426c53e0846edf","tid":2266609,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}